\c 33
\s Basa renharirire
\p
\v 1 Zvino shoko raJehovha rakasvika kwandiri richiti:
\v 2 Mwanakomana wemunhu, taura kuvana vevanhu vako, uti kwavari: Pandinouisa munondo pamusoro penyika, kana vanhu venyika iyo vakatora munhu pamiganhu yavo vakamuita nharirire yavo,
\v 3 paanoona munondo uchiuya pamusoro penyika, akaridza hwamanda ndokuyambira vanhu;
\v 4 zvino ani nani anonzwa kurira kwehwamanda akasayambirika, kana munondo ukauya ukamubvisa, ropa rake richava pamusoro pemusoro wake.
\v 5 Wakanzwa kurira kwehwamanda, akasayambirika, ropa rake richava pamusoro pake, asi anoyambirika achaponesa mweya wake.
\v 6 Asi kana nharirire ichiona munondo uchiuya ikasaridza hwamanda, vanhu ndokusayambira, kana munondo ukauya ukabvisa munhu pakati pavo, wabviswa nechivi chake asi ropa rake richatsvakwa muruoko rwenharirire.
\p
\v 7 Saizvozvowo iwe mwanakomana wemunhu, ndakakuisa kuva nharirire kuimba yaIsraeri; naizvozvo uchanzwa shoko pamuromo wangu ugovanyeverera ini.
\v 8 Kana ndichiti kune wakaipa: Iwe wakaipa, uchafa zvirokwazvo, kana iwe ukasataura kuti uyambire wakaipa kubva panzira yake, wakaipa uyo achafira muchivi chake, asi ropa rake ndicharitsvaka paruoko rwako.
\v 9 Asi kana iwe ukayambira wakaipa panzira yake kuti abve pairi, kana akasatendeuka panzira yake, iye achafira muchivi chake, asi iwe wanunura mweya wako.
\p
\v 10 Naizvozvo iwe, mwanakomana wemunhu, iti kuimba yaIsraeri: Imwi munotaura seizvi muchiti: Nokuti zvitadzo zvedu nezvivi zvedu zviri pamusoro pedu, uye tinopera mazviri; zvino tichararama sei?
\v 11 Uti kwavari: Neupenyu hwangu, anoreva Ishe Jehovha handifariri rufu rwewakaipa, asi kuti wakaipa atendeuke panzira yake ararame. Tendeukai, tendeukai panzira dzenyu dzakaipa, nokuti muchafirei, imwi imba yaIsraeri?
\p
\v 12 Zvino iwe, mwanakomana wemunhu, uti kuvana vevanhu vako: Kururama kwewakarurama hakungamununuri pazuva rekudarika kwake; uye kana kuri kuipa kwewakaipa haangawi nako pazuva raakatendeuka kubva pauipi hwake, uye wakarurama haangararami ne\add kururama kwake\add* nezuva raanotadza.
\v 13 Pandichati kune wakarurama uchararama zvirokwazvo, kana iye achivimba nekururama kwake, ndokuita chitadzo, kururama kwake kwese hakungarangarirwi; asi nekuda kweuipi hwake hwaaita, achahufira.
\v 14 Uye kana ndichiti kune wakaipa: Uchafa zvekufa; kana akatendeuka kubva pachivi chake, ndokuita mutongo nekururama;
\v 15 wakaipa akadzosa rubatso, akaripa zvakapambiwa, akafamba muzvimiso zveupenyu, kuti asaita chitadzo, achararama zvirokwazvo, haangafi.
\v 16 Hakuna chimwe chezvivi zvake zvaakaita chicharangarirwa kwaari; waita mutongo nekururama achararama zvirokwazvo.
\p
\v 17 Asi vana vevanhu vako vanoti: Nzira yaIshe haina kururama; asi kana vari ivo, nzira yavo ndiyo isina kururama.
\v 18 Kana wakarurama akatendeuka kubva pakururama kwake ndokuita chitadzo, achafawo nekuda kwacho.
\v 19 Asi kana wakaipa akatendeuka kubva pauipi hwake, ndokuita mutongo nekururama, iye achararama naizvozvo.
\p
\v 20 Zvakadaro munoti: Nzira yaIshe haina kururama. Haiwa imba yaIsraeri, ndichakutongai umwe neumwe zvichitevera nzira dzake.
\s Kuwa kweJerusarema
\p
\v 21 Zvino zvakaitika mugore regumi nemaviri reutapwa hwedu, mu\add mwedzi\add* wegumi, nereshanu remwedzi, umwe waiva apukunyuka kubva muJerusarema wakasvika kwandiri achiti: Guta rarohwa.
\v 22 Zvino ruoko rwaJehovha rwaiva pamusoro pangu madekwani, wakapukunyuka asati asvika; zvino wakashamisa muromo wangu, kusvika iye asvika kwandiri mangwanani; muromo wangu ukashama, ndikasazova mbeveve.
\p
\v 23 Zvino shoko raJehovha rikasvika kwandiri, richiti:
\v 24 Mwanakomana wemunhu, vagari vematongo awo enyika yaIsraeri vanotaura vachiti: Abhurahama waiva ari umwe, akagara nhaka yenyika; asi isu tiri vazhinji, nyika yapiwa isu kuva nhaka.
\v 25 Naizvozvo iti kwavari: Anoreva seizvi Ishe Jehovha: Munodya zvine ropa, uye munosimudzira meso enyu kuzvifananidzo zvenyu nekuteura ropa; zvino muchagara nhaka yenyika here?
\v 26 Munomira pamusoro pemunondo wenyu, munoita chinyangadzo, uye makasvibisa umwe neumwe mukadzi wewekwake, zvino muchagara nhaka yenyika iyo here?
\v 27 Reva seizvi kwavari: Anoreva seizvi Ishe Jehovha: Neupenyu hwangu, zvirokwazvo vari mumatongo vachawa nemunondo, naiye ari mubani ndichapa kuzvikara kuti adyiwe; nevari munhare nemumapako vachafa nehosha.
\v 28 Nyika ndichaiita dongo nekuparara, uye kuzvikudza kwemasimba ayo kuchapera, nemakomo aIsraeri achava matongo, kuti kusava neanopfuura \add nepo\add*.
\v 29 Zvino vachaziva kuti ndiri Jehovha, kana ndaita nyika dongo kwazvo nekuda kwezvinyangadzo zvavo zvese zvavakaita.
\p
\v 30 Zvino iwe, mwanakomana wemunhu, vana vevanhu vako vanokutaura vari pamasvingo nepamikova yedzimba, vanotaura umwe kune umwe vachiti umwe neumwe kuhama yake: Huya hako, unzwe shoko rinobuda kuna Jehovha.
\v 31 Zvino vanouya kwauri sekuuya kwevanhu, uye vanogara pamberi pako se\add zvinoita\add* vanhu vangu, vanonzwa mashoko ako, asi havaaiti; nokuti vanoratidza rudo rukoro nemuromo wavo, moyo wavo unotevera mibairo yavo yakaipa.
\v 32 Zvino tarira, iwe wakaita kwavari serwiyo rwunodikanwa, shoko rinotapira, uye unogona kuridza zvakanaka mbira, nokuti vanonzwa mashoko ako, asi havaaiti.
\v 33 Zvino pakusvika kweizvi, (tarira zvichasvika), ipapo vachaziva kuti muporofita wanga ari pakati pavo.
